text: Robert Booth (born 26 March 1964) is an Australian rower. He competed in the men's coxless pair event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Australian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Australia Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
